strings: <voice_0x01001C59><se_high>Media princess: However, if you drink a lot of water, you will stay full.
<voice_0x01001C5A><se_high>Media princess: I hate to say it, but I guess I need to stop drinking for a while.
<voice_0x01001C5B><se_high>Media princess: Go a little longer and drink again... Ha!
